org.sql: SELECT spree_product_properties.* FROM spree_product_properties INNER JOIN spree_properties ON spree_properties.id = spree_product_properties.property_id INNER JOIN spree_products ON spree_products.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_products.id = spree_product_properties.product_id WHERE spree_product_properties.id IN ("$1", "$2") AND spree_properties.filterable = "$3" AND spree_products.deleted_at IS NULL ORDER BY spree_product_properties.position ASC

rewrites.sql: SELECT spree_product_properties.* FROM spree_product_properties INNER JOIN spree_properties ON spree_properties.id = spree_product_properties.property_id INNER JOIN spree_products ON spree_products.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_products.id = spree_product_properties.product_id WHERE spree_product_properties.id IN ("$1", "$2") AND spree_properties.filterable = "$3" AND spree_products.deleted_at IS NULL ORDER BY spree_product_properties.position ASC LIMIT 1
